-- London & Regional Properties Eyes Greek Hellenikon, Ta Nea Says
-- B y   P a u l   T u g w e l l
-- 2012-04-20T09:44:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-20/london-regional-properties-eyes-greek-hellenikon-ta-nea-says.html
U.K.-based London & Regional
Properties, the Qatar Investment Authority and  Israel ’s Gazit-
Globe Ltd. and  Elbit Systems Ltd (ESLT)  are among the nine groups that
expressed interest in  Greece ’s Hellenikon SA,  Ta Nea  said.  The other groups interested in buying Hellenikon SA, which
will develop and exploit the site of the former Athens
International Airport, are Greece’s  Lamda Development SA (LAMDA) , a
Spanish real-estate company, a venture made up of Cypriot
interests, another Qatari fund and Trump Organization Inc., the
Athens-based newspaper reported today, without citing anyone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
